<paragraph id="8B9936C2CA74FF9BC96638C0FC65FAC2" blockId="36.[769,1357,1150,1571]" pageId="36" pageNumber="655">The Egyptian Weasel has often been considered conspecific with the Least Weasel, but is now recognized as a separate species. Monotypic.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
